title: Microsoft Azure AddOn: Machine Extension
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/Microsoft
license: GPLv2
distribution: Christopher Pommer
description:
 This check monitors the provisioning state of the Azure extensions installed
 on Azure Arc machines and Azure VMs.

 Depending on the configured service state levels for the available
 Azure extension provisioning states, the service is {OK}, {WARN}, {CRIT} or {UNKNOWN}.

 You have to configure the special agent {Microsoft Azure AddOn}.

discovery:
 One service is created for all extensions on the host.
